IMPORTANT NOTICE

Please review the README at the following location before proceeding!

https://github.com/habitat-sh/on-prem-builder

The following migrations may be required:

For installations prior to June 15, 2018:
* Package migration from file system to Minio store

For installations prior to August 17, 2018
* Database migration to merge shards

For installations prior to September 24th, 2018
* Database merge to a single 'builder' database

Further details can be found in the README.
